<!--
The FakeXMB was made to look like the official Playstation 3 XMB, and has an information bar very similar to the Top-Info of the Playstation-X theme.
It has monochrome logos in the system view, used in various themes and with various colors, in our case just gray, used mainly in RVGM-BT.
FakeXMB is a free theme and can be used on your preferred system.
Enjoy!
Special thanx: Pajarorojo, Fabrice Caruso and Darknior.
Theme: FakeXMB
author: LordOgro
license: creative commons CC-BY-NC-SA
-->
